### Get a token for a regular user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@clicknback.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass"
}

### 200 – Happy path: list active offers (first page, default page size)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: list active offers with explicit page and page_size
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page=1&page_size=3
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: second page (verifies pagination slicing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page=2&page_size=3
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 200 – Happy path: page beyond total (expects empty offers array)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page=99
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 200 – Boundary: minimum valid page size
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page_size=1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 200 – Boundary: maximum valid page size
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page_size=10
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 422 – Invalid: page=0 (below minimum)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page=0
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 422 – Invalid: page_size=0 (below minimum)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page_size=0
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 422 – Invalid: page_size=101 (above maximum, assuming max_page_size=100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active?page_size=101
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 401 – Missing or expired token
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/active
